description:
Get a unique entertainment experience and enjoy your favorites movies and TV Shows, find all genres from Action and War to Romance and Comedy and much more.

The app will help you to find the right movie for you using smart features and intelligent recommendations, you can also watch the movie trailer with an exceptional experience of the Augmented Reality.

FEATURES:

- Clean UI that will help you find your movies easily.
- Movies are structured into well refined categories (Popular, Trending ...)
- Get notifications and stay updated with the movie you love.
- Advanced & smart search (Find movies, shows, actors ...).
- Get movies details, trailers, cast, similar & recommendations.
- The app learns while you use it so you will get customized recommendations for you.
- You can watch all movies trailers normally or using the Augmented Reality technology.

- This app is not for streaming/watching movies.
- All movies/shows information and images/data are from TMDB.org API licensed under CC BY-NC 4.0: (https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc/4.0/) and according to their terms of use: (https://www.themoviedb.org/documentation/api/terms-of-use).

- Discover Now Playing / Popular / Top / Trending / Upcoming / Best Of Years Movies & TV Shows
- Quick search for movies and TV series by title
- Watch trailers and other videos
- Create your own watchlists for movies
- TV series calendar
- Detailed information about movies and TV series
- Rate Movies/TV shows in app and explore other rating
- Complete list of episodes for TV series with complete information about the episodes
- Search for services where you can buy, rent, stream films and series
- Watch videos (HD fullsreen) about movies and TV shows without leaving the app
- Profiles of actors with their full filmography
- Simple and user-friendly application interface
- Browsing history
- No account required

Disclaimer: 
In the application, you cannot watch films and series for free, but you can find in the application a complete description of the series and films and also the service on which you can watch them.

All movies information and images are from TMDB.org licensed under CC BY-NC 4.0: https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc/4.0/

This app uses the TMDb API but is not endorsed or certified by TMDb: https://www.themoviedb.org/documentation/api/terms-of-use

HappyMood – Discover Games Made for You

Are you a true gamer looking for one place to explore everything about games? HappyMoods is your ultimate companion! With a huge database of games, you can easily search, discover, and enjoy all the details you need in one simple app.
Explore a Massive Library HappyMood Browse through a wide range of games across different styles and categories. Whether you love action, adventure, puzzle, or strategy, HappyMods brings everything together in one place.
Watch Trailers & Gameplay Before playing, get a real taste of the game! Watch trailers and gameplay videos to see exactly what the game looks like.
Save Your Favorites HappyMood Build your own personalized collection of favorite games. Add the ones you love and come back to them anytime.
Track Games You Like Never lose track of a game again. Follow the games you’re interested in and keep them organized in your list.
Choose Your Mood Not sure what to play? Select your mood and HappyMod will recommend games that match how you feel at that moment. Fun, relaxing, scary, or exciting – there’s always a game waiting for you.
Test Your Knowledge Think you know everything about games? Try our quiz and challenge yourself with fun questions to see how much of a gaming expert you are.
All-in-One Gaming Experience HappyMood makes it easy for you to discover new games, keep track of your favorites, enjoy videos, and even test your knowledge. It’s everything a gamer needs – simple, clear, and always fun.
With HappyMod, finding the perfect game has never been easier.

Presentamos la nueva WebNovel: ¡tu puerta de entrada a emocionantes aventuras! Sumérgete en un mundo de novelas cautivadoras y embárcate en viajes inolvidables. Estamos aquí para redefinir la forma en que experimenta la lectura en línea: leamos sus aventuras.

Descubre un tesoro escondido de géneros novedosos que te transportarán a reinos más allá de tu imaginación. Sumérgete en las maravillas de la fantasía occidental, donde deambulan criaturas míticas y se desarrollan misiones épicas. Disfrute del encanto de la fantasía oriental, con fascinantes historias de wuxia, xianxia, xuanhuan y más. Piérdete en el encanto de las novelas fantásticas que te mantendrán hechizado de principio a fin.
Pero eso no es todo: tenemos algo especial para los fanáticos de las novelas de sistema, los litRPG y la fantasía de progresión. Experimenta la emoción de subir de nivel y desbloquear nuevos poderes junto a tus personajes favoritos mientras navegan por mundos inmersivos similares a los de un juego.

Con WebNovel, tienes acceso a una vasta biblioteca de novelas cautivadoras, escritas por autores talentosos de todo el mundo. Nuestra interfaz intuitiva garantiza una experiencia de lectura perfecta, permitiéndole sumergirse por completo en cada giro y giro.

Comience su viaje de lectura hoy con WebNovel, donde cada página es una invitación a escapar de la realidad y embarcarse en misiones extraordinarias. ¡Prepárate para leer tus aventuras como nunca antes!

Géneros destacados: Misterio, Fantasía oriental, Fantasía occidental, Ciencia ficción, Fan-fic, Xianxia, Xuanhuan, Wuxia, Romance, Mangas de aventuras, Cómics, Manhua, Webtoon
Novelas Originales y Exclusivas: Mago Supremo, Mi sistema vampírico. Esclavo de las sombras
Novelas traducidas y exclusivas: Biblioteca del camino al cielo, El señor de los misterios, Ella se vuelve glamorosa después de la anulación del compromiso
Cómic exclusivo/Manga/Manhua/Manhwa/Webtoon: La Bella y la Bestia, Cuando la Bella se encuentra con las Bestias

Únase a miles de aspirantes a autores. Comience su viaje contando sus historias en WebNovel. "El viaje de mil millas comienza con un solo paso". Únase a nuestro concurso quincenal de sugerencias de escritura y publique su novela con nuestro sistema de emparejamiento para millones de lectores que comparten un interés similar en su género. Encuentra tu voz y comparte tu mensaje con el mundo.

Muchos géneros de libros te esperan para explorar en la aplicación WebNovel.
